text: The 83rd Infantry Division (, 83-ya Pekhotnaya Diviziya) was an infantry formation of the Russian Imperial Army. ==Organization== *1st Brigade **329th Infantry Regiment **330th Infantry Regiment *2nd Brigade **331st Infantry Regiment **332nd Infantry Regiment ==Commanders== *July-November 1914: Konstantin Lukich Gilchevsky ==References== Category:Infantry divisions of the Russian Empire
